---
import Layout from "../layouts/Layout.astro";

const title = "Privacy Policy — BoatHaven";
const description = "Read the BoatHaven Privacy Policy.";
---

<Layout title={title} description={description}>
  <div class="mx-auto max-w-3xl px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 py-12">
    <h1 class="text-3xl font-extrabold text-text mb-8">Privacy Policy</h1>

    <div class="prose prose-gray max-w-none text-text-muted space-y-6">
      <p><strong>Last updated:</strong> March 2026</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">1. Information We Collect</h2>
      <p>We collect information you provide when creating an account (name, email, profile photo), booking details, messages between users, and usage data through cookies and analytics.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">2. How We Use Your Information</h2>
      <p>Your information is used to provide and improve the platform, process bookings, facilitate communication between users, and send relevant notifications.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">3. Information Sharing</h2>
      <p>We share your information only with other users as necessary for bookings (e.g., your name with a boat owner), service providers who assist platform operations, and when required by law.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">4. Data Security</h2>
      <p>We use industry-standard security measures to protect your data, including encryption in transit and secure storage through Firebase/Google Cloud infrastructure.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">5. Your Rights</h2>
      <p>You may access, update, or delete your personal data through your account settings. You may also request a copy of your data or ask us to stop processing it by contacting us.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">6. Cookies</h2>
      <p>We use essential cookies for authentication and session management. Third-party analytics cookies may be used to understand platform usage.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">7. Changes to This Policy</h2>
      <p>We may update this policy from time to time. We will notify users of significant changes via email or platform notification.</p>

      <h2 class="text-xl font-bold text-text">8. Contact</h2>
      <p>For privacy-related questions, please <a href="/contact" class="text-primary hover:underline">contact us</a>.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</Layout>
